                    "kind": "text",
                    "data": "By default: **4 results** per request.\n\nConfigurable via the `maxResults` parameter:\n- Default: `4` (set by `docs-mcp.default-max-results=4` in application.properties)\n- Max allowed: `50`\n\nExamples:\n```json\n{\"query\": \"fiber routing\"}                    → 4 results (default)\n{\"query\": \"fiber routing\", \"maxResults\": 2}   → 2 results\n{\"query\": \"fiber routing\", \"maxResults\": 10}  → 10 results\n{\"query\": \"fiber routing\", \"maxResults\": 99}  → capped at 50\n```\n\nWant me to change the default?"
                  }
