            "data": "The new chunker works well:\n\n- **Before**: 311 chunks, purely character-based splits\n- **After**: 268 chunks, header-aware with section titles preserved\n\nKey improvements:\n- Each chunk starts with its **section title** (e.g., \"Route Handlers\", \"Anatomy of a route\")\n- Small sections stay intact (no unnecessary splits)\n- Large sections get subdivided but keep the title prefix for context\n- Average chunk size is ~408 chars (sections <1000 chars stay whole, larger ones get split at ~500)\n\nLet me re-run the full pipeline and e2e test to confirm everything still works:"
