            "data": "Here's what's currently indexed (minimal test set — 1-2 docs per framework):\n\n| Framework | Source Repo | Docs Fetched | Chunks |\n|-----------|------------|--------------|--------|\n| Go Fiber | `gofiber/fiber` | `docs/guide/routing.md`, `docs/api/ctx.md` | 268 |\n| Go Gin | `gin-gonic/gin` | `docs/doc.md` | 181 |\n| Go Echo | `labstack/echo` | `README.md` | 32 |\n| FastAPI | `fastapi/fastapi` | `tutorial/first-steps.md`, `tutorial/path-params.md` | 56 |\n| Express | `expressjs/express` | `Readme.md` | 27 |\n| NestJS | `nestjs/docs.nestjs.com` | `content/controllers.md`, `content/providers.md` | 69 |\n| Rocket | `rwf2/Rocket` | `site/guide/2-getting-started.md`, `site/guide/4-requests.md` | 189 |\n| Actix-web | `actix/actix-web` | `README.md`, `actix-web/README.md` | 14 |\n| Django | `django/django` | `docs/intro/tutorial01.txt`, `docs/topics/http/urls.txt` | 122 |\n| Flask | `pallets/flask` | `docs/quickstart.rst`, `docs/blueprints.rst` | 116 |\n| ASP.NET Core | `dotnet/AspNetCore.Docs` | `fundamentals/routing.md`, `fundamentals/middleware/index.md` | 425 |\n| Spring Boot | `spring-projects/spring-boot` | `web/servlet.adoc`, `data/sql.adoc` | 192 |\n| Spring Framework | `spring-projects/spring-framework` | `core/beans/definition.adoc`, `web/webmvc.adoc` | 65 |\n| Spring Security | `spring-projects/spring-security` | `authentication/architecture.adoc`, `authorization/authorize-http-requests.adoc` | 181 |\n| Spring Data | `spring-projects/spring-data-jpa` | `jpa/query-methods.adoc` | 107 |\n| Spring Cloud | `spring-cloud/spring-cloud-gateway` | `how-it-works.adoc`, `configuring-route-predicate-factories...adoc` | 5 |\n\n**Total: 2,049 chunks** from 26 markdown/asciidoc/rst files across 16 frameworks.\n\nThis is the minimal test set. To get full coverage you'd expand the `paths` lists in each scraper to include all the documentation pages (routing, middleware, authentication, database, testing, deployment, etc.)."
