          {
            "kind": "text",
            "data": "As you can see — it returns results from `definition.adoc` which covers bean factories and XML-based DI, but not `@Autowired` annotation-style injection.\n\nThat's because we only indexed 2 files for Spring Framework:\n- `core/beans/definition.adoc` ← this one (bean definitions)\n- `web/webmvc.adoc` (web MVC)\n\nThe actual `@Autowired` / annotation-based DI content lives in `core/beans/dependencies.adoc` and `core/beans/annotation-config.adoc` which we didn't include in the minimal test set.\n\nThe search **is working correctly** — it found the most relevant content about \"dependency injection\" from what's available. It just needs more docs. Want me to add the missing Spring DI documentation files to the scraper and re-run?"
          }
        ]
